            //   Check: −R55·ψq/(xq'−xq'') = −ψq/Tq0'' ✓
            //
            // −Ed'/Tq0'': inter-winding coupling
            //   = −[(xq−xl)/Tq0''] · [Ed'/(xq−xl)] = J54 · ∂H/∂Ed'
            //   So J[5,4] = −(xq−xl)/Tq0'' and J[4,5] = +(xq−xl)/Tq0'' (skew)
