            //                                  and ∂H/∂Eq' = Eq'/(xd−xl)
            //   Wait: −R[2,2]·∂H/∂Eq' = −(1/Td0')·Eq'/(xd−xl)·(xd−xl) = −Eq'/Td0' ✓
            //   ... but we need R[2,2]·(xd−xl) = (xd−xl)/Td0'? No.
